summary: Adds an Khajiit Assassin Merchant to Riften.
descriptionHtml:
A small, but useful mod, which I first created for myself only, but decided to share with you!
So this mod adds a Khajiit Merchant to Bee and Barb, in Riften. He sells different daggers (iron, steel, glass, elven and ebony) and also some light armor (Leather gear and Scaled gear, no helmets)
He is in the basement of the Inn (Bee and Barb in Riften as I said)
I hope you will find this usefull, I might add some other items, you can leave suggestions in the comment section.

If you find a bug, inform me.
Mod made by me, khzuOVG.

Screenshots coming soon, not much to show though.
